title: kungen12321
author: kungen12321
content: Hi!I am repairing a s17pro hashboard. On domain 4 I dont have power, 0.8v but not 1.8v. Were to continue the diagnostic to find the problem?Thanks in advance!

comments.author: BitMaxz
comments.body: What domain 4 are you talking about is that the voltage domain? But what exactly?There are 5 testpoints on the hashboard if you want to diagnose the issue there is a manual repair guide from Zeusbtc you can maybe get some idea of how to fix them check the link below.- https://www.zeusbtc.com/manuals/Antminer-S17-Hash-Board-Repair-Guide.asp
